plany-zajec-czerwiec.description:
LESSON PLANS FOR THE ENTIRE JUNE correlated with PDF materials from the SUMMER set
Each of the plans is developed for three age groups: toddlers (3 years old), middle group (4 years old), and seniors (5-6 years old). There are 8 of them, so they are perfect if English is taught in each group twice a week.
What do the lesson plans contain?
- vocabulary and phrases to be introduced in individual classes;
- class topic to be entered into the record book (formulated partly in English and partly in the native language);
- a list of necessary materials in a convenient check-off list - templates, cards, or worksheets for printing available in the PDF set for this season
- class procedure with detailed steps
Lesson plans are the perfect solution for you if…
- you are a committed teacher and would like to have more energy during classes without having to spend hours on their prior preparation;
- you want to gain additional time by receiving a ready-to-use curriculum and topics to enter into the record book;
- you have purchased a PDF materials set and would like to discover even more ways to use it

